data.description: Spacious 2-story home with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a 2 car detached garage, on a large, double corner lot. Home features a Living Room and a Family Room. All appliances included. Rooms have been virtually staged. Home was used as a rental, therefore, there is not a Homestead exemption deducted from the property taxes. The property taxes may be lower if someone purchases this home as an Owner Occupant. Home is on a crawl space. New Central Air unit and furnace 2022.  New windows, new roof, new gutters 2015. Close to schools and shopping.
